description: The fastest Bun Slinger in Texas is buckin’ his truck through town and wrangling all the appetites around with a hearty selection of franks and sausages with toppings so tasty, it’s no wonder this chuck is everyone’s ‘most wanted’. Come saddle on up to this truck and hog-tie yourself a “Winchester”- Jumbo Hebrew National Kosher All Beef Frank, or a “Colt 45 ”- Pork Jalapeno Sausage Wrapped in a Tortilla- and heap on your choice of chili, cheese, sautéed onions, mustard, jalapeños, or Bun Slinger’s own Trail Blazin’ Frank Sauce- it’s fired up with enough flavor and spice to even knock Jesse James’ spurs right off and send him right outta dodge. And If you’re fixin’ to throw a big hoedown, be sure to invite Bun Slinger, and your guests will certainly be impressed by all his great chow.  Whether you’re a cowboy, outlaw, or even a yankee, you’ll find the grub at Wild West Franks to be the darn tootin’ best.
name: Wild West Franks
